00:07:18.139 --> 00:07:20.840 line:93%
Kebiasaan seseorang tidak akan sering berubah.

00:07:21.710 --> 00:07:23.040 line:93%
Pimpinan Jo

00:07:24.509 --> 00:07:26.480 line:93%
