Ruang kontrol.

00:09:15.689 --> 00:09:18.490 line:93%
Si Penikam Putar masuk ke sana?

00:09:19.020 --> 00:09:20.229 line:93%
Bagaimana bisa?

00:09:20.859 --> 00:09:22.429 line:93%
Pimpinan dan aku membuat kesepakatan.

00:09:24.760 --> 00:09:28.030 line:93%
Seseorang akan menyusup malam ini.

00:09:28.900 --> 00:09:30.500 line:93%
Biarkan dia masuk.

00:09:30.500 --> 00:09:33.209 line:93%
- Kamu membujuk Pimpinan? /- Ya.

00:09:33.969 --> 00:09:35.670 line:93%
Kita bisa menangkapnya saat dia keluar?

00:09:35.670 --> 00:09:36.880 line:93%
Tidak.

00:09:37.339 --> 00:09:40.780 line:93%
Kita menangkapnya saat dia menyerahkan barang itu ke bosnya.

00:09:40.780 --> 00:09:43.420 line:93%
Dua orang sekaligus?

00:09:57.329 --> 00:09:58.559 line:93%
Apa itu?

00:09:59.260 --> 00:10:01.670 line:93%
Salah satu barang milik si Penikam Putar

00:10:02.030 --> 00:10:03.370 line:93%
