00:10:08.209 --> 00:10:09.780 line:93%
Apa? Yang mana...

00:10:10.140 --> 00:10:13.380 line:93%
Pelacak yang itu ada di dalam tubuhku...

00:10:15.109 --> 00:10:16.479 line:93%
