00:10:16.849 --> 00:10:20.189 line:93%
Hei, aku juga mau. Di mana kamu mendapatkannya? Apakah mahal?

00:10:24.260 --> 00:10:27.229 line:93%
Itu dia. Sekarang, pukul aku.

00:10:27.530 --> 00:10:29.859 line:93%
- Apa? /- Seperti saat itu.

00:10:29.859 --> 00:10:31.630 line:93%
Keras dan sekali pukul, paham?

00:10:31.630 --> 00:10:33.729 line:93%
Kamu ingin aku memukulmu lagi?

00:10:34.229 --> 00:10:36.439 line:93%
Otakmu bermasalah?

00:10:37.870 --> 00:10:39.170 line:93%
Aku suka ini.

00:10:49.410 --> 00:10:50.620 line:93%
Bagus.

00:10:52.420 --> 00:10:54.920 line:93%
- Kamu baik-baik saja? /- Aku baik...

00:10:55.920 --> 00:10:57.520 line:93%
Kenapa aku merasa lemah sekali sekarang?

00:10:57.520 --> 00:10:59.620 line:93%
Serahkan kepadaku. Pergilah ke rumah sakit.

00:11:02.229 --> 00:11:03.729 line:93%
Kamu juga.

00:11:03.959 --> 00:11:05.359 line:93%
Terus kabari aku.

00:11:07.099 --> 00:11:09.069 line:93%
Kamu bicara dengan siapa?

00:11:09.130 --> 00:11:10.270 line:93%
"Layanan Penghubung Genesis"

00:11:18.679 --> 00:11:20.309 line:93%
"Mengirim perintah"

00:11:20.309 --> 00:11:21.349 line:93%
"Terkirim"

00:11:21.550 --> 00:11:23.750 line:93%
"Sistem menyala"

00:11:38.699 --> 00:11:42.170 line:93%
- Ayo. /- Lalu kenapa dia mengajakku?

00:11:42.370 --> 00:11:44.339 line:93%
Dia bicara dengan siapa?

00:11:44.339 --> 00:11:46.709 line:93%
Denganku. Bisa kita pergi? Aku kelelahan.

00:12:02.150 --> 00:12:03.290 line:93%
