00:13:36.750 --> 00:13:38.550 line:93%
- Sungguh? /- Ya.

00:14:12.319 --> 00:14:13.750 line:93%
Di mana Jin Soo A?

00:14:15.420 --> 00:14:16.689 line:93%
Aku kehilangan dia,

00:14:18.420 --> 00:14:20.089 line:93%
tapi aku tahu tujuannya.

00:14:49.349 --> 00:14:51.260 line:93%
Aku hampir terlambat.

00:14:51.260 --> 00:14:52.819 line:93%
Dia bisa muncul.

00:14:53.390 --> 00:14:54.829 line:93%
Apa pun yang terjadi,

00:14:55.490 --> 00:14:57.859 line:93%
- lindungi Gong Soo Chang. /- Jangan khawatir.

00:14:57.859 --> 00:14:59.829 line:93%
Jika melihat si Penikam Putar itu,

00:14:59.829 --> 00:15:01.069 line:93%
aku akan membunuhnya.

00:15:01.069 --> 00:15:05.069 line:93%
Kamu si Penikam putar dari Jepang?

00:15:05.540 --> 00:15:07.270 line:93%
Jadi, kamu wanita.

00:15:07.270 --> 00:15:08.609 line:93%
Senang bertemu denganmu.

00:15:09.309 --> 00:15:13.679 line:93%
Lihat, aku juga mahir menggunakan pisau.

00:15:13.679 --> 00:15:16.719 line:93%
Ayo serang aku. Karena kamu wanita,

00:15:16.719 --> 00:15:18.819 line:93%
aku tidak akan terlalu kasar kepadamu.

00:15:24.059 --> 00:15:26.829 line:93%
Astaga. Bangun! Cepat!

00:15:26.829 --> 00:15:29.630 line:93%
Kejar dia! Dia tidak boleh lepas!

00:15:29.630 --> 00:15:31.630 line:93%
Kenapa kita melakukan ini?

00:15:31.630 --> 00:15:34.829 line:93%
Soo Chang, bertahanlah. Lakukan itu demi teman satu selmu.

00:15:35.130 --> 00:15:38.140 line:93%
Kamu teman satu selnya? Kamu pernah dipenjara?

00:15:52.550 --> 00:15:54.750 line:93%
Kita harus bicara.

00:16:00.630 --> 00:16:02.559 line:93%
Kamu membunuh Hang Joo.

00:16:09.800 --> 00:16:11.740 line:93%
Dia bagaikan keluarga untukku.

00:17:20.639 --> 00:17:22.069 line:93%
Jin Soo A!

00:17:28.109 --> 00:17:30.020 line:93%
Kamu berhak untuk tetap diam.

00:17:30.919 --> 00:17:33.250 line:93%
Kamu bisa menyewa pengacara

00:17:33.250 --> 00:17:35.119 line:93%
dan menolak memberikan pernyataan yang memberatkan.

00:17:38.490 --> 00:17:39.619 line:93%
Aku sangat

00:17:40.930 --> 00:17:42.829 line:93%
berharap kamu melakukan itu.

00:17:44.859 --> 00:17:47.069 line:93%
Aku ingin kamu tetap diam

00:17:47.069 --> 00:17:49.129 line:93%
dan merenungkan perbuatanmu

00:17:49.129 --> 00:17:51.440 line:93%
untuk waktu yang sangat lama.

00:17:51.440 --> 00:17:53.109 line:93%
Suatu hari, kamu akan sadar

00:17:56.510 --> 00:17:59.010 line:93%
seberat apa pun penderitaanmu,

00:18:02.809 --> 00:18:04.849 line:93%
kamu membuat orang lain menderita juga.

00:18:21.399 --> 00:18:24.500 line:93%
Jalanlah lebih dahulu, aku harus menemui teman.

00:18:24.500 --> 00:18:25.540 line:93%
Baiklah.

00:18:45.290 --> 00:18:46.530 line:93%
Kamu sungguh menangkapnya.

00:18:47.889 --> 00:18:48.930 line:93%
Ya.

00:18:50.159 --> 00:18:51.700 line:93%
Kita menangkapnya bersama.

00:18:53.329 --> 00:18:54.869 line:93%
Sekarang bagaimana?

00:18:56.230 --> 00:18:57.270 line:93%
Jin Soo A

00:18:57.270 --> 00:18:59.200 line:93%
akan didakwa atas pembunuhan Hang Joon, Kim Jong Doo,

00:18:59.500 --> 00:19:01.210 line:93%
