00:19:01.839 --> 00:19:03.109 line:93%
Dia akan disidang.

00:19:03.210 --> 00:19:04.510 line:93%
Lantas Kepala Jaksa Tak?

00:19:04.510 --> 00:19:08.710 line:93%
Jika dia bersaksi bahwa Kepala Tak menghasut pembunuhan itu,

00:19:09.510 --> 00:19:11.550 line:93%
Kepala Jaksa Tak tidak akan bisa bebas.

00:19:11.720 --> 00:19:13.550 line:93%
Kurasa semua sudah berakhir.

00:19:15.950 --> 00:19:17.260 line:93%
Itu bagus.

00:19:18.119 --> 00:19:20.530 line:93%
Sekarang aku bisa kembali.

00:19:20.930 --> 00:19:22.059 line:93%
Ya.

00:19:25.230 --> 00:19:26.369 line:93%
Kalau begitu

00:19:27.270 --> 00:19:28.500 line:93%
aku pergi.

00:19:31.899 --> 00:19:33.569 line:93%
Sampai jumpa, Adik Hantu.

00:19:33.869 --> 00:19:36.780 line:93%
- Jangan abaikan aku saat melihatku. /- Kamu gila.

00:19:37.079 --> 00:19:40.210 line:93%
Aku gila? Kamu lebih gila bicara dengan hantu.

